Package: LSExperiment
Title: Author Factorial Survey Experiments for LimeSurvey with LimeSeed
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Stefan", "Munnes", , "stefan.munnes@wzb.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create and edit factorial survey experiments for LimeSurvey using a YAML file that contains all dimensions and levels. This package uses this structured information to automatically populate your LimeSeed. Additional preview and export functions are available.
